#
# If you have an Android phone or tablet, you will be attracted to the convenience and powerfulness of Android App Widget.
# But sometimes it's hard to find the very Widget you need, and sometimes you just don't like the way existing Widgets are.
#
# The AAWW project aims at solving these problems.
# AAWW (Android App Widget Wizard) is designed to provide Android users with a simple way to DIY Android App Widgets.
# On the AAWW web platform, you can easily create your favorite application shortcuts, browser bookmarks, fast dial, etc, or a combination of them.
#

#
# Here is the instruction of AAWW:
# 
# Step 1: Visit http://162.105.81.63
#
# Step 2: Input the name of the Widget, size of the Widget, and finally your name. And press "START!"
#
# Step 3: Design the Layout in the workspace, creating new components from the component library
#
# Step 4: Adjust the position and size of the component with your mouse, and edit other attributes of the component with your keyboard
#
# Step 5: Upload some resource pictures to customize the appearance of the widget
#
# Step 6: Edit the function of each component and check the logic of each component
#
# Step 7: Confirm everything, and you can sumbit your widget configuration to the server
#
# Step 8: Wait for the apk file to download; install it on your Android device.
# 
# Step 9: Enjoy!
#

#
# Enjoy Yourself About AAWW!
#
